<col><b>Hydric oxide</b></col> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>, <cd>water.</cd> --
<col><b>Hydric sulphate</b></col> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>, <cd>hydrogen
sulphate or sulphuric acid.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

